dct_title_s: Extract from an unfinished map of Saugor & Nurbudda States : Scale 8 miles = 1 inch
dct_description_sm: 15th. November 1860.; Hand colored boundaries and routes.; Relief shown by hand shading.; Vide map of the country bordering the Great Trunk Road between Benares and Delhi.; Vide map of the country south of Ganges.; Vide map of Rajpootana Sheet Number6.; Copied by Sunawullah, finished & examined by J.O.N. James Surveyor Generals Office Calcutta November 1860.
81 x 151 Centimeters, folded to  27 x 18 Centimeters
Ames Library of South Asia Maps
